cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.RO, cs.SY, cs.CV 

This paper deals with reinforcement learning and inverse reinforcement learning, which are core topics in machine learning and artificial intelligence. The use of options and the focus on multitasking operations suggest that the paper is likely to be categorized under cs.LG (Machine Learning) and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). The use of optimization methods and the focus on robotics suggest that the paper may also be categorized under cs.RO (Robotics and Control Systems). The use of feature spaces and the potential application to computer vision suggest that the paper may also be categorized under cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). Finally, the paper's focus on system-level performance and robustness suggests that it may also be categorized under cs.SY (Systems and Control).
